703577f-a.title: Brooklyn: Clark Street - Henry Street
703577f-a.text:
109-111 Clark Street, between Henry and Fulton Streets. (In the
foreground, is seen Monroe Place, a short street beginning at Clark Street,
and running west to the East River).
April 13, 1931.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(u)
The same, showing the same view nine years earlier.
1922.
Augene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
